# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root .gitignore — VeriLearn monorepo
# The actual app lives in web/ (which has its own .gitignore too).
# This file guards the repo ROOT against build/dependency junk.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies (regenerated with `npm install`; pinned by package-lock.json)
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
.pnp
.pnp.*

# Next.js build output & traces (regenerated by `next build`/`next dev`)
.next/
**/.next/
out/
**/out/

# Test / tooling caches
.vite/
**/.vite/
coverage/
**/coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Production build artifacts
build/
dist/

# Environment / secrets (never commit these)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem

# Editor / OS cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
